1
00:00:06,450 --> 00:00:07,450
<font color="yellow">(Episode 39)</font>

2
00:00:14,220 --> 00:00:15,890
<font color="yellow">Why is this photo here?</font>

3
00:00:18,950 --> 00:00:19,990
<font color="yellow">Was Soo Yeon...</font>

4
00:00:20,590 --> 00:00:21,950
<font color="yellow">an employee here?</font>

5
00:00:23,250 --> 00:00:24,400
<font color="yellow">Yes.</font>

6
00:00:24,400 --> 00:00:25,650
<font color="yellow">Were Soo Yeon...</font>

7
00:00:26,320 --> 00:00:28,450
<font color="yellow">and I this close?</font>

8
00:00:29,020 --> 00:00:30,260
<font color="yellow">Well...</font>

9
00:00:30,260 --> 00:00:31,320
<font color="yellow">Kang Gi Tan.</font>

10
00:00:42,350 --> 00:00:44,120
<font color="yellow">I'm going to marry Soo Yeon.</font>

11
00:00:47,790 --> 00:00:48,850
<font color="yellow">So...</font>

12
00:00:49,720 --> 00:00:51,650
<font color="yellow">forget about her.</font>

13
00:01:00,220 --> 00:01:02,290
<font color="yellow">I just got out of the meeting.</font>

14
00:01:02,920 --> 00:01:04,290
<font color="yellow">I'll come by the office.</font>

15
00:01:05,520 --> 00:01:07,590
<font color="yellow">Okay, Mr Min.</font>

16
00:01:09,050 --> 00:01:10,090
<font color="yellow">Soo Yeon.</font>

17
00:01:11,420 --> 00:01:13,250
<font color="yellow">Chairman wants to see you.</font>

18
00:01:14,050 --> 00:01:15,660
<font color="yellow">Where is he?</font>

19
00:01:16,450 --> 00:01:17,930
<font color="yellow">Congratulations.</font>

20
00:01:17,930 --> 00:01:20,620
<font color="yellow">I heard you patented the MK2 vaccine.</font>

21
00:01:21,190 --> 00:01:22,850
<font color="yellow">- What about it?
-  I'd like...</font>

22
00:01:23,350 --> 00:01:24,490
<font color="yellow">to buy the patent.</font>

23
00:01:26,320 --> 00:01:27,890
<font color="yellow">You were right.</font>

24
00:01:37,050 --> 00:01:39,490
<font color="yellow">Why are you here, Soo Yeon?</font>

25
00:01:39,490 --> 00:01:40,520
<font color="yellow">I called her.</font>

26
00:01:40,950 --> 00:01:42,190
<font color="yellow">Join us, Lawyer Oh.</font>

27
00:01:43,020 --> 00:01:44,590
<font color="yellow">If you don't need me here...</font>

28
00:01:44,590 --> 00:01:46,050
<font color="yellow">We're talking business.</font>

29
00:01:46,720 --> 00:01:47,820
<font color="yellow">We'd feel comfortable...</font>

30
00:01:48,350 --> 00:01:49,850
<font color="yellow">with a legal representative.</font>

31
00:01:54,090 --> 00:01:55,890
<font color="yellow">It's fine. Have a seat.</font>

32
00:02:02,920 --> 00:02:05,290
<font color="yellow">Lawyer Oh, let me ask you something.</font>

33
00:02:06,590 --> 00:02:08,650
<font color="yellow">It's about B World, Il Jae's old company.</font>

34
00:02:09,320 --> 00:02:11,020
<font color="yellow">Did you know Gun Woo purchased it?</font>

35
00:02:15,620 --> 00:02:16,690
<font color="yellow">You didn't.</font>

36
00:02:18,720 --> 00:02:20,620
<font color="yellow">How did you take over?</font>

37
00:02:21,950 --> 00:02:24,920
<font color="yellow">Is it wrong to acquire a company?</font>

38
00:02:25,320 --> 00:02:26,490
<font color="yellow">It's not.</font>

39
00:02:27,620 --> 00:02:29,720
<font color="yellow">I find it odd that Il Jae sold his goose...</font>

40
00:02:30,720 --> 00:02:32,690
<font color="yellow">that lays golden eggs to you.</font>

41
00:02:33,820 --> 00:02:35,220
<font color="yellow">Don't you, Lawyer Oh?</font>

42
00:02:38,350 --> 00:02:39,620
<font color="yellow">This is what I think.</font>

43
00:02:40,020 --> 00:02:43,580
<font color="yellow">Either he and Il Jae had some sort of a deal,</font>

44
00:02:43,580 --> 00:02:45,390
<font color="yellow">or Il Jae was threatened by him...</font>

45
00:02:45,390 --> 00:02:47,220
<font color="yellow">and had no choice...</font>

46
00:02:47,220 --> 00:02:50,190
<font color="yellow">but to hand over the company.</font>

47
00:02:51,450 --> 00:02:54,590
<font color="yellow">The B World information you gave Lawyer Oh before the trial...</font>

48
00:02:55,820 --> 00:02:57,950
<font color="yellow">If I'm right, those files were meaningless.</font>

49
00:02:58,420 --> 00:03:00,690
<font color="yellow">I think you kept the real deal...</font>

50
00:03:01,520 --> 00:03:03,750
<font color="yellow">and used it to threaten Il Jae.</font>

51
00:03:06,690 --> 00:03:08,400
<font color="yellow">Your novel's quite appealing.</font>

52
00:03:08,400 --> 00:03:09,490
<font color="yellow">But...</font>

53
00:03:09,950 --> 00:03:11,510
<font color="yellow">in exchange for B World,</font>

54
00:03:11,510 --> 00:03:13,950
<font color="yellow">I gave up the home shopping channel and golf course.</font>

55
00:03:15,720 --> 00:03:17,820
<font color="yellow">Isn't that a reasonable deal?</font>

56
00:03:17,820 --> 00:03:19,220
<font color="yellow">It was a foolish one.</font>

57
00:03:20,120 --> 00:03:21,650
<font color="yellow">Once the MK2 vaccine's released,</font>

58
00:03:22,620 --> 00:03:24,340
<font color="yellow">B World will go down.</font>

59
00:03:24,340 --> 00:03:26,180
<font color="yellow">That's why I made an offer.</font>

60
00:03:26,180 --> 00:03:28,080
<font color="yellow">I want to buy the patent...</font>

61
00:03:28,080 --> 00:03:29,290
<font color="yellow">for the MK2 vaccine.</font>

62
00:03:30,820 --> 00:03:31,820
<font color="yellow">You know that...</font>

63
00:03:32,250 --> 00:03:33,590
<font color="yellow">I won't sell it.</font>

64
00:03:34,590 --> 00:03:35,650
<font color="yellow">Gi Tan.</font>

65
00:03:35,990 --> 00:03:38,450
<font color="yellow">If B World goes down, Dodo Pharmaceutical...</font>

66
00:03:38,820 --> 00:03:39,820
<font color="yellow">will take a hit.</font>

67
00:03:40,450 --> 00:03:42,050
<font color="yellow">Attacking the holding company...</font>

68
00:03:42,050 --> 00:03:44,450
<font color="yellow">means you want to start a war against Dodo Group.</font>

69
00:03:45,890 --> 00:03:48,090
<font color="yellow">I'm running a legitimate business.</font>

70
00:03:49,150 --> 00:03:50,520
<font color="yellow">The threat to Dodo Pharmaceutical...</font>

71
00:03:51,450 --> 00:03:54,150
<font color="yellow">is the result of your foolish transactions.</font>

72
00:03:54,590 --> 00:03:55,650
<font color="yellow">We're done talking.</font>

73
00:03:56,820 --> 00:03:59,660
<font color="yellow">I tried to give you a way out.</font>

74
00:03:59,660 --> 00:04:02,590
<font color="yellow">An obedient donkey gets a carrot.</font>

75
00:04:02,590 --> 00:04:03,800
<font color="yellow">But an insolent one...</font>

76
00:04:03,800 --> 00:04:04,990
<font color="yellow">gets a whipping.</font>

77
00:04:06,350 --> 00:04:08,190
<font color="yellow">I hold the rein...</font>

78
00:04:09,420 --> 00:04:10,790
<font color="yellow">and you're my donkey.</font>

79
00:04:25,020 --> 00:04:27,790
<font color="yellow">Why didn't you tell me you'd taken over B World?</font>

80
00:04:30,120 --> 00:04:32,510
<font color="yellow">As your legal counsel, I had to know.</font>

81
00:04:32,510 --> 00:04:34,820
<font color="yellow">You know I was busy with the general meeting.</font>

82
00:04:34,820 --> 00:04:37,720
<font color="yellow">You could have told me after the general meeting.</font>

83
00:04:38,620 --> 00:04:41,690
<font color="yellow">Don't tell me you believe all that nonsense.</font>

84
00:04:44,250 --> 00:04:47,360
<font color="yellow">I'm looking for evidence of Il Jae's corruption.</font>

85
00:04:48,790 --> 00:04:52,050
<font color="yellow">Why do you think I paid so much for his company?</font>

86
00:04:52,520 --> 00:04:54,680
<font color="yellow">Embezzlement, tax fraud, illegal lobbying.</font>

87
00:04:54,680 --> 00:04:56,550
<font color="yellow">If I find proof of these,</font>

88
00:04:57,120 --> 00:05:00,360
<font color="yellow">I can lock him up for good at his upcoming appeal.</font>

89
00:05:01,620 --> 00:05:04,550
<font color="yellow">I'll give you the files as soon as I find them.</font>

90
00:05:05,220 --> 00:05:09,620
<font color="yellow">So don't believe the script Gi Tan wrote.</font>

91
00:05:25,150 --> 00:05:26,190
<font color="yellow">Soo Tak.</font>

92
00:05:26,920 --> 00:05:27,990
<font color="yellow">Mr Moon.</font>

93
00:05:30,020 --> 00:05:31,220
<font color="yellow">We're listening.</font>

94
00:05:32,320 --> 00:05:33,920
<font color="yellow">Lawyer Oh and I...</font>

95
00:05:36,050 --> 00:05:37,190
<font color="yellow">How close were we?</font>

96
00:05:39,320 --> 00:05:40,990
<font color="yellow">The photo we saw...</font>

97
00:05:42,050 --> 00:05:44,990
<font color="yellow">shows that we weren't always this polite.</font>

98
00:05:45,790 --> 00:05:47,550
<font color="yellow">What happened between...</font>

99
00:05:48,690 --> 00:05:50,520
<font color="yellow">Lawyer Oh and me?</font>

100
00:05:51,820 --> 00:05:54,450
<font color="yellow">You two were very close.</font>

101
00:05:55,790 --> 00:05:56,920
<font color="yellow">"Very close"?</font>

102
00:05:58,520 --> 00:06:00,220
<font color="yellow">How close do you mean?</font>

103
00:06:04,720 --> 00:06:07,690
<font color="yellow">When you were framed for murder and on the run,</font>

104
00:06:08,820 --> 00:06:11,620
<font color="yellow">Lawyer Oh tried very hard to clear your name.</font>

105
00:06:13,220 --> 00:06:14,420
<font color="yellow">And that is why...</font>

106
00:06:14,950 --> 00:06:16,020
<font color="yellow">her brother died.</font>

107
00:06:16,990 --> 00:06:17,990
<font color="yellow">Her brother died...</font>

108
00:06:18,820 --> 00:06:19,990
<font color="yellow">because of me?</font>

109
00:06:21,020 --> 00:06:23,220
<font color="yellow">It wasn't your fault exactly.</font>

110
00:06:23,790 --> 00:06:26,050
<font color="yellow">- Il Jae...
-  That's the same thing!</font>

111
00:06:33,520 --> 00:06:34,720
<font color="yellow">Why did you...</font>

112
00:06:35,590 --> 00:06:37,350
<font color="yellow">keep this from me?</font>

113
00:06:39,620 --> 00:06:42,720
<font color="yellow">The memories of her are the cause of your headaches.</font>

114
00:06:43,690 --> 00:06:46,420
<font color="yellow">That's why Professor Jin erased them.</font>

115
00:06:47,320 --> 00:06:48,850
<font color="yellow">I don't remember anything.</font>

116
00:06:49,690 --> 00:06:51,500
<font color="yellow">Don't try to, Sir.</font>

117
00:06:51,500 --> 00:06:52,850
<font color="yellow">The headaches might return.</font>

118
00:06:54,790 --> 00:06:55,920
<font color="yellow">Is that all?</font>

119
00:06:56,820 --> 00:06:57,910
<font color="yellow">What do you mean?</font>

120
00:06:57,910 --> 00:06:59,390
<font color="yellow">About my relationship with her.</font>

121
00:06:59,790 --> 00:07:00,820
<font color="yellow">Is that it?</font>

122
00:07:02,820 --> 00:07:03,820
<font color="yellow">I think you were close...</font>

123
00:07:04,420 --> 00:07:05,990
<font color="yellow">since you started as colleagues.</font>

124
00:07:06,520 --> 00:07:07,520
<font color="yellow">That is...</font>

125
00:07:08,420 --> 00:07:09,490
<font color="yellow">all we know, Sir.</font>

126
00:07:19,190 --> 00:07:20,490
<font color="yellow">Chairman Do is here.</font>

127
00:07:26,890 --> 00:07:29,720
<font color="yellow">Are you working on getting rid of my wife's allies?</font>

128
00:07:29,720 --> 00:07:33,120
<font color="yellow">We have a list of names and reasons to fire them all.</font>

129
00:07:33,120 --> 00:07:35,290
<font color="yellow">Gather them all.</font>

130
00:07:35,890 --> 00:07:36,920
<font color="yellow">Yes, Father.</font>

131
00:07:56,250 --> 00:07:58,750
<font color="yellow">I plan to shuffle the personnel around...</font>

132
00:07:59,620 --> 00:08:01,420
<font color="yellow">including all the CEOs.</font>

133
00:08:02,320 --> 00:08:05,290
<font color="yellow">Thank you for working for and putting up with...</font>

134
00:08:06,450 --> 00:08:08,220
<font color="yellow">such an incompetent chairwoman.</font>

135
00:08:09,190 --> 00:08:10,650
<font color="yellow">It's time you all retire.</font>

136
00:08:12,420 --> 00:08:15,070
<font color="yellow">What do you mean, Sir?</font>

137
00:08:15,070 --> 00:08:16,320
<font color="yellow">You're all fired.</font>

138
00:08:17,790 --> 00:08:18,910
<font color="yellow">Hand in your resignation letters.</font>

139
00:08:18,910 --> 00:08:20,300
<font color="yellow">This is unfair.</font>

140
00:08:20,300 --> 00:08:21,820
<font color="yellow">It's too sudden.</font>

141
00:08:22,190 --> 00:08:23,220
<font color="yellow">CEO Hong.</font>

142
00:08:23,820 --> 00:08:26,680
<font color="yellow">At your daughter's wedding, a supplier gave you...</font>

143
00:08:26,680 --> 00:08:28,490
<font color="yellow">50,000 dollars in the form of a gift.</font>

144
00:08:31,220 --> 00:08:32,220
<font color="yellow">CEO Yang.</font>

145
00:08:33,120 --> 00:08:36,750
<font color="yellow">You sent your wife and her family on a trip, and got reimbursed for it.</font>

146
00:08:38,520 --> 00:08:39,520
<font color="yellow">CEO Cho.</font>

147
00:08:40,050 --> 00:08:43,660
<font color="yellow">You bought an apartment for a female supplier.</font>

148
00:08:43,660 --> 00:08:45,190
<font color="yellow">Does your wife know about it?</font>

149
00:08:46,590 --> 00:08:49,460
<font color="yellow">The first mistake Gwi Ja made...</font>

150
00:08:50,750 --> 00:08:53,620
<font color="yellow">was placing disloyal men like you in key positions,</font>

151
00:08:54,790 --> 00:08:56,420
<font color="yellow">thinking that you'd be of help.</font>

152
00:08:57,590 --> 00:08:59,190
<font color="yellow">Of course, the root will rot...</font>

153
00:08:59,720 --> 00:09:02,090
<font color="yellow">if the water is rotten.</font>

154
00:09:03,220 --> 00:09:04,880
<font color="yellow">If you do not turn in...</font>

155
00:09:04,880 --> 00:09:07,690
<font color="yellow">your resignation letters within this morning,</font>

156
00:09:08,920 --> 00:09:11,490
<font color="yellow">the police will find out...</font>

157
00:09:12,990 --> 00:09:16,190
<font color="yellow">about all these disgusting things you've done.</font>

158
00:09:16,190 --> 00:09:17,650
<font color="yellow">The choice is yours.</font>

159
00:09:26,290 --> 00:09:29,320
<font color="yellow">Reinstate all CEOs of our subsidiaries...</font>

160
00:09:30,120 --> 00:09:32,330
<font color="yellow">whom Gwi Ja fired.</font>

161
00:09:32,330 --> 00:09:33,390
<font color="yellow">Yes, Father.</font>

162
00:09:38,960 --> 00:09:42,550
<font color="yellow">Why is Mr Han still here?</font>

163
00:09:44,020 --> 00:09:47,590
<font color="yellow">I will be loyal to you, Chairman. Please give me another chance.</font>

164
00:09:48,090 --> 00:09:50,570
<font color="yellow">He helped out significantly during the general meeting.</font>

165
00:09:50,570 --> 00:09:53,520
<font color="yellow">He can do a lot of things, so please leave him to me.</font>

166
00:09:54,490 --> 00:09:57,220
<font color="yellow">Gun Woo, you need to get a promotion, too.</font>

167
00:09:57,220 --> 00:09:59,620
<font color="yellow">I am satisfied with what I have.</font>

168
00:09:59,620 --> 00:10:03,690
<font color="yellow">I will promote you as the vice chairman.</font>

169
00:10:06,220 --> 00:10:07,350
<font color="yellow">Oh, right.</font>

170
00:10:08,490 --> 00:10:12,220
<font color="yellow">What is this about your marrying Lawyer Oh?</font>

171
00:10:13,290 --> 00:10:15,720
<font color="yellow">I understand that she's a good woman,</font>

172
00:10:16,420 --> 00:10:18,590
<font color="yellow">but she's not someone for you to marry.</font>

173
00:10:20,720 --> 00:10:24,620
<font color="yellow">My in-law needs to be one of the best families in Korea.</font>

174
00:10:27,590 --> 00:10:29,890
<font color="yellow">It's probably a rumour made by the reporters.</font>

175
00:10:30,650 --> 00:10:32,020
<font color="yellow">I have never...</font>

176
00:10:32,920 --> 00:10:34,960
<font color="yellow">thought about marrying Lawyer Oh.</font>

177
00:10:36,120 --> 00:10:37,190
<font color="yellow">Good.</font>

178
00:10:38,620 --> 00:10:40,050
<font color="yellow">Remember this, Gun Woo.</font>

179
00:10:40,750 --> 00:10:41,820
<font color="yellow">You are...</font>

180
00:10:42,650 --> 00:10:44,150
<font color="yellow">the next chairman...</font>

181
00:10:45,990 --> 00:10:47,650
<font color="yellow">who'll lead Dodo Group.</font>

182
00:10:48,350 --> 00:10:49,420
<font color="yellow">Yes, Father.</font>

183
00:10:55,990 --> 00:10:58,450
<font color="yellow">Congratulations on your promotion.</font>

184
00:10:59,390 --> 00:11:01,490
<font color="yellow">Congratulations, Vice Chairman.</font>

185
00:11:04,090 --> 00:11:07,090
<font color="yellow">(Oh Soo Yeon)</font>

186
00:11:14,450 --> 00:11:17,450
<font color="yellow">That means CEO Do took over B World to help you.</font>

187
00:11:18,120 --> 00:11:20,920
<font color="yellow">He gave up the home shopping channel and the golf course.</font>

188
00:11:21,520 --> 00:11:24,020
<font color="yellow">Lawyer Oh, you should grasp his heart...</font>

189
00:11:24,020 --> 00:11:25,790
<font color="yellow">while you have the chance.</font>

190
00:11:26,450 --> 00:11:28,580
<font color="yellow">No, thanks. Stop saying that.</font>

191
00:11:28,580 --> 00:11:31,820
<font color="yellow">Look around. You won't find anyone like him.</font>

192
00:11:32,490 --> 00:11:36,520
<font color="yellow">I really respect him as a fellow man...</font>

193
00:11:36,520 --> 00:11:38,690
<font color="yellow">for what he does to you, Lawyer Oh.</font>

194
00:11:39,520 --> 00:11:42,140
<font color="yellow">Gi Tan helped out Soo Yeon a lot, too.</font>

195
00:11:42,140 --> 00:11:43,220
<font color="yellow">Right, Soo Yeon?</font>

196
00:11:43,750 --> 00:11:47,090
<font color="yellow">Who cares? He has no memory of her.</font>

197
00:11:47,090 --> 00:11:49,790
<font color="yellow">They are as good as strangers.</font>

198
00:11:50,220 --> 00:11:53,020
<font color="yellow">It's still left in Soo Yeon's memories.</font>

199
00:11:53,020 --> 00:11:55,090
<font color="yellow">That's the problem.</font>

200
00:11:55,590 --> 00:11:59,020
<font color="yellow">She is the only one who's suffering from this.</font>

201
00:11:59,950 --> 00:12:01,850
<font color="yellow">There's a song that goes like this.</font>

202
00:12:03,090 --> 00:12:11,020
<font color="yellow">If love hurts you a lot, it probably wasn't love at all.</font>

203
00:12:11,450 --> 00:12:13,190
<font color="yellow">That's not how you sing it.</font>

204
00:12:13,190 --> 00:12:15,120
<font color="yellow">Don't ruin a perfectly good song.</font>

205
00:12:15,820 --> 00:12:16,890
<font color="yellow">I'm sorry.</font>

206
00:12:16,890 --> 00:12:20,220
<font color="yellow">It's simply because I'm drunk.</font>

207
00:12:21,090 --> 00:12:22,320
<font color="yellow">Why isn't he coming?</font>

208
00:12:23,450 --> 00:12:24,890
<font color="yellow">Who else is coming?</font>

209
00:12:25,520 --> 00:12:28,070
<font color="yellow">What? Well...</font>

210
00:12:28,070 --> 00:12:29,150
<font color="yellow">Who is it?</font>

211
00:12:29,790 --> 00:12:31,910
<font color="yellow">Well...</font>

212
00:12:31,910 --> 00:12:33,820
<font color="yellow">Cheers, guys.</font>

213
00:12:49,350 --> 00:12:51,790
<font color="yellow">- Chairman.
-  You can go home.</font>

214
00:13:04,820 --> 00:13:06,220
<font color="yellow">CEO Do, you're here.</font>

215
00:13:07,120 --> 00:13:08,650
<font color="yellow">How did you find us?</font>

216
00:13:09,390 --> 00:13:10,790
<font color="yellow">I called him.</font>

217
00:13:10,790 --> 00:13:13,620
<font color="yellow">I asked him to pay for our little gathering.</font>

218
00:13:16,820 --> 00:13:19,120
<font color="yellow">Who's the guy you called?</font>

219
00:13:19,590 --> 00:13:21,520
<font color="yellow">Oh, no one.</font>

220
00:13:22,450 --> 00:13:24,920
<font color="yellow">- CEO Do, have a drink.
-  Sure.</font>

221
00:13:25,920 --> 00:13:28,130
<font color="yellow">You don't have to use both hands.</font>

222
00:13:28,130 --> 00:13:29,590
<font color="yellow">(Soo Tak...)</font>

223
00:13:34,350 --> 00:13:37,720
<font color="yellow">Soo Tak, I don't think Gi Tan should come today.</font>

224
00:13:41,750 --> 00:13:45,320
<font color="yellow">Chairman, Nan Jeong says that you shouldn't come today.</font>

225
00:13:47,720 --> 00:13:49,650
<font color="yellow">Let's leave for today, Sir.</font>

226
00:14:00,950 --> 00:14:01,990
<font color="yellow">Let's go.</font>

227
00:14:10,890 --> 00:14:12,990
<font color="yellow">You didn't have to walk me home.</font>

228
00:14:13,520 --> 00:14:14,690
<font color="yellow">Have you...</font>

229
00:14:15,620 --> 00:14:17,120
<font color="yellow">given it a thought?</font>

230
00:14:18,820 --> 00:14:22,050
<font color="yellow">About asking you to marry me...</font>

231
00:14:25,820 --> 00:14:29,390
<font color="yellow">I am very thankful for it and I know that I don't deserve it.</font>

232
00:14:30,550 --> 00:14:32,820
<font color="yellow">- But Gun Woo, I...
-  My father...</font>

233
00:14:33,750 --> 00:14:34,750
<font color="yellow">told me today...</font>

234
00:14:37,020 --> 00:14:38,420
<font color="yellow">that I can marry you.</font>

235
00:14:39,890 --> 00:14:42,740
<font color="yellow">I was also appointed as the vice chairman, too.</font>

236
00:14:42,740 --> 00:14:46,220
<font color="yellow">My father's health is failing, so he won't be around for long.</font>

237
00:14:46,650 --> 00:14:48,720
<font color="yellow">So can we at least get engaged?</font>

238
00:14:49,420 --> 00:14:52,220
<font color="yellow">- Gun Woo...
-  I only live like a crazy man...</font>

239
00:14:52,990 --> 00:14:54,120
<font color="yellow">because of you.</font>

240
00:14:57,020 --> 00:14:58,220
<font color="yellow">You just have to make the decision.</font>

241
00:15:00,090 --> 00:15:01,220
<font color="yellow">I'll wait for the answer.</font>

242
00:15:34,220 --> 00:15:35,320
<font color="yellow">Chairman.</font>

243
00:15:35,950 --> 00:15:37,050
<font color="yellow">Hello.</font>

244
00:15:37,820 --> 00:15:38,920
<font color="yellow">I am Kang Gi Tan.</font>

245
00:15:39,820 --> 00:15:42,420
<font color="yellow">I am Lawyer Oh Soo Yeon. Nice to meet you.</font>

246
00:15:55,650 --> 00:15:57,690
<font color="yellow">It feels like you're avoiding me on purpose.</font>

247
00:15:58,520 --> 00:15:59,590
<font color="yellow">Am I wrong?</font>

248
00:15:59,950 --> 00:16:01,090
<font color="yellow">It's not like that.</font>

249
00:16:11,050 --> 00:16:12,620
<font color="yellow">I'm going to marry Soo Yeon.</font>

250
00:16:13,220 --> 00:16:14,350
<font color="yellow">So...</font>

251
00:16:16,020 --> 00:16:17,850
<font color="yellow">forget about her.</font>

252
00:16:19,720 --> 00:16:20,720
<font color="yellow">Chairman!</font>

253
00:16:23,050 --> 00:16:24,120
<font color="yellow">Are you okay?</font>

254
00:16:36,950 --> 00:16:38,550
<font color="yellow">You look troubled.</font>

255
00:16:39,350 --> 00:16:40,790
<font color="yellow">Is this because of Lawyer Oh?</font>

256
00:16:41,420 --> 00:16:42,490
<font color="yellow">Thanks to you,</font>

257
00:16:43,620 --> 00:16:45,120
<font color="yellow">I feel much better.</font>

258
00:16:46,720 --> 00:16:48,120
<font color="yellow">How is your headache?</font>

259
00:16:49,190 --> 00:16:50,220
<font color="yellow">I'm okay.</font>

260
00:16:51,120 --> 00:16:52,150
<font color="yellow">That's a relief.</font>

261
00:16:53,750 --> 00:16:56,050
<font color="yellow">I just received a call from someone in SPD.</font>

262
00:16:56,920 --> 00:16:57,990
<font color="yellow">He said Gun Woo is...</font>

263
00:16:58,890 --> 00:17:00,320
<font color="yellow">promoted as the vice chairman.</font>

264
00:17:02,450 --> 00:17:05,220
<font color="yellow">- We have to make a move...
-  How is the vaccine received...</font>

265
00:17:05,920 --> 00:17:07,350
<font color="yellow">among pharmaceutical companies?</font>

266
00:17:07,350 --> 00:17:09,190
<font color="yellow">Geukdong Pharmaceutical is the most interested.</font>

267
00:17:10,120 --> 00:17:12,620
<font color="yellow">They were always behind Dodo Pharmaceutical.</font>

268
00:17:14,690 --> 00:17:17,950
<font color="yellow">- I'll seal the deal tomorrow.
-  Yes, Sir.</font>

269
00:17:20,660 --> 00:17:23,090
<font color="yellow">This new MK2 vaccine is...</font>

270
00:17:23,090 --> 00:17:26,750
<font color="yellow">much more effective and cheaper...</font>

271
00:17:26,750 --> 00:17:30,490
<font color="yellow">than mutant influenza vaccine produced by Dodo Pharmaceutical.</font>

272
00:17:30,490 --> 00:17:33,800
<font color="yellow">This is the opening of a new generation of vaccines.</font>

273
00:17:33,800 --> 00:17:37,190
<font color="yellow">Dodo Pharmaceutical has always defended their position on top,</font>

274
00:17:37,190 --> 00:17:41,660
<font color="yellow">but things do not look promising thanks to this brand new vaccine.</font>

275
00:17:42,020 --> 00:17:45,320
<font color="yellow">The fall of Dodo Pharmaceutical will affect the entire group.</font>

276
00:17:46,390 --> 00:17:49,660
<font color="yellow">Vice Chairman Do, what's our plan?</font>

277
00:17:50,160 --> 00:17:52,220
<font color="yellow">There is one way to walk out of this crisis.</font>

278
00:17:52,690 --> 00:17:55,660
<font color="yellow">We'll put some of our subsidiaries through a paid-in capital increase.</font>

279
00:17:56,620 --> 00:17:59,190
<font color="yellow">- Paid-in capital increase?
-  Yes.</font>

280
00:17:59,190 --> 00:18:01,350
<font color="yellow">Based on last year's sales,</font>

281
00:18:01,350 --> 00:18:03,820
<font color="yellow">we'll issue new stock shares...</font>

282
00:18:03,820 --> 00:18:05,320
<font color="yellow">for companies that lost money.</font>

283
00:18:12,220 --> 00:18:14,420
<font color="yellow">Ga Din, I'm in a meeting now.</font>

284
00:18:14,420 --> 00:18:16,020
<font color="yellow">What's a "paid-in capital increase"?</font>

285
00:18:17,420 --> 00:18:19,920
<font color="yellow">Gun Woo will put out Dodo Hotel for a paid-in capital increase.</font>

286
00:18:20,350 --> 00:18:22,920
<font color="yellow">That will damage the percentage of your shares.</font>

287
00:18:27,220 --> 00:18:28,520
<font color="yellow">Shin Young, it's me.</font>

288
00:18:28,520 --> 00:18:30,450
<font color="yellow">Walk out of the room and talk to me.</font>

289
00:18:35,420 --> 00:18:37,630
<font color="yellow">I'm outside. You can talk.</font>

290
00:18:37,630 --> 00:18:41,590
<font color="yellow">That means he'll issue new Dodo Hotel stocks.</font>

291
00:18:42,750 --> 00:18:44,090
<font color="yellow">What will happen then?</font>

292
00:18:44,420 --> 00:18:46,690
<font color="yellow">If Gun Woo gets those shares,</font>

293
00:18:47,220 --> 00:18:48,220
<font color="yellow">your ownership of the hotel...</font>

294
00:18:49,320 --> 00:18:50,450
<font color="yellow">could be threatened.</font>

295
00:18:51,020 --> 00:18:52,020
<font color="yellow">What?</font>

296
00:18:52,720 --> 00:18:54,390
<font color="yellow">He's up to something then.</font>

297
00:18:55,390 --> 00:18:57,120
<font color="yellow">We have to stop the recapitalisation.</font>

298
00:18:57,920 --> 00:18:58,920
<font color="yellow">Can you do that?</font>

299
00:18:59,790 --> 00:19:01,450
<font color="yellow">Don't worry. Trust me.</font>

300
00:19:05,050 --> 00:19:08,110
<font color="yellow">Dodo Corporation, Dodo Insurance, Dodo Engineering...</font>

301
00:19:08,110 --> 00:19:10,520
<font color="yellow">and Dodo Hotel will be recapitalised.</font>

302
00:19:14,620 --> 00:19:15,660
<font color="yellow">Not the hotel.</font>

303
00:19:20,320 --> 00:19:22,890
<font color="yellow">For as long as I'm around, there's no way you can...</font>

304
00:19:22,890 --> 00:19:24,120
<font color="yellow">recapitalise on the hotel.</font>

305
00:19:24,750 --> 00:19:26,920
<font color="yellow">You lost over 10 million dollars last year.</font>

306
00:19:26,920 --> 00:19:28,320
<font color="yellow">If you keep going...</font>

307
00:19:28,320 --> 00:19:30,390
<font color="yellow">Don't be like that, Vice Chairman.</font>

308
00:19:30,820 --> 00:19:32,420
<font color="yellow">Don't mention last year's numbers.</font>

309
00:19:32,790 --> 00:19:35,890
<font color="yellow">Don't you know I turned it around since I took over this year?</font>

310
00:19:36,920 --> 00:19:39,990
<font color="yellow">Sir, Dodo Hotel must be recapitalised.</font>

311
00:19:40,790 --> 00:19:42,590
<font color="yellow">Why are we in this mess?</font>

312
00:19:43,020 --> 00:19:44,610
<font color="yellow">It's because you bought B World...</font>

313
00:19:44,610 --> 00:19:46,660
<font color="yellow">and that threatened Dodo Pharmaceutical.</font>

314
00:19:47,420 --> 00:19:50,100
<font color="yellow">Why are you trying to make someone else pay the price?</font>

315
00:19:50,100 --> 00:19:52,350
<font color="yellow">Gi Tan has the patent to the MK2 vaccine.</font>

316
00:19:52,890 --> 00:19:54,710
<font color="yellow">Why did you sign...</font>

317
00:19:54,710 --> 00:19:56,720
<font color="yellow">a Shareholders' Voting Agreement with our enemy?</font>

318
00:19:57,920 --> 00:19:58,920
<font color="yellow">What?</font>

319
00:20:00,950 --> 00:20:03,050
<font color="yellow">That's because I plan...</font>

320
00:20:03,890 --> 00:20:04,890
<font color="yellow">to marry him.</font>

321
00:20:08,220 --> 00:20:09,750
<font color="yellow">What are you talking about?</font>

322
00:20:10,290 --> 00:20:12,660
<font color="yellow">I'm going to marry Kang Gi Tan.</font>

323
00:20:13,220 --> 00:20:14,310
<font color="yellow">Shin Young...</font>

324
00:20:14,310 --> 00:20:15,550
<font color="yellow">It's not a bad idea.</font>

325
00:20:18,320 --> 00:20:19,520
<font color="yellow">He's involved in many of our transactions,</font>

326
00:20:20,050 --> 00:20:21,920
<font color="yellow">including the shipbuilding deal.</font>

327
00:20:23,220 --> 00:20:24,660
<font color="yellow">If Shin Young were to marry him,</font>

328
00:20:24,660 --> 00:20:26,820
<font color="yellow">that would help us overcome this crisis.</font>

329
00:20:28,660 --> 00:20:30,220
<font color="yellow">We can discuss this later.</font>

330
00:20:31,320 --> 00:20:32,550
<font color="yellow">Let's conclude this meeting.</font>

331
00:20:39,320 --> 00:20:40,320
<font color="yellow">Shin Young.</font>

332
00:20:40,890 --> 00:20:42,520
<font color="yellow">You manage a hotel.</font>

333
00:20:43,020 --> 00:20:44,590
<font color="yellow">Don't you know what recapitalisation is?</font>

334
00:20:45,720 --> 00:20:47,420
<font color="yellow">I studied fashion.</font>

335
00:20:47,820 --> 00:20:51,390
<font color="yellow">Have you heard of "windowpane gingham check patterns"?</font>

336
00:20:51,390 --> 00:20:53,090
<font color="yellow">You don't make clothes.</font>

337
00:20:53,750 --> 00:20:57,090
<font color="yellow">If you want to be my partner, start studying.</font>

338
00:20:57,090 --> 00:20:58,120
<font color="yellow">Studying?</font>

339
00:21:01,120 --> 00:21:02,990
<font color="yellow">I can do that.</font>

340
00:21:03,590 --> 00:21:05,890
<font color="yellow">However, you need to be the one to teach me.</font>

341
00:21:05,890 --> 00:21:08,020
<font color="yellow">I'm not bored enough to tutor you.</font>

342
00:21:08,020 --> 00:21:10,840
<font color="yellow">Do it. I want to study hard...</font>

343
00:21:10,840 --> 00:21:11,920
<font color="yellow">with you.</font>

344
00:21:12,590 --> 00:21:14,920
<font color="yellow">She wants to study, not have fun.</font>

345
00:21:14,920 --> 00:21:16,220
<font color="yellow">Say yes, Sir.</font>

346
00:21:17,790 --> 00:21:18,820
<font color="yellow">Very well.</font>

347
00:21:19,290 --> 00:21:20,660
<font color="yellow">- I'll teach you.
-  Really?</font>

348
00:21:21,890 --> 00:21:23,930
<font color="yellow">No homework or exams.</font>

349
00:21:23,930 --> 00:21:25,820
<font color="yellow">Then I'll really study hard.</font>

350
00:21:28,120 --> 00:21:30,020
<font color="yellow">How did you prevent the recapitalisation?</font>

351
00:21:30,020 --> 00:21:32,660
<font color="yellow">I told my dad that I'd marry you.</font>

352
00:21:37,390 --> 00:21:38,790
<font color="yellow">He didn't object.</font>

353
00:21:39,750 --> 00:21:40,820
<font color="yellow">When should we get married?</font>

354
00:21:41,720 --> 00:21:42,850
<font color="yellow">This autumn?</font>

355
00:21:44,720 --> 00:21:47,390
<font color="yellow">We'll go on our honeymoon in the Mediterranean.</font>

356
00:21:47,390 --> 00:21:50,990
<font color="yellow">Mr Moon, I think you should tutor her.</font>

357
00:21:50,990 --> 00:21:52,290
<font color="yellow">Sorry?</font>

358
00:21:52,290 --> 00:21:54,300
<font color="yellow">Are you going back on your promise?</font>

359
00:21:54,300 --> 00:21:56,560
<font color="yellow">I'm too scared to teach you.</font>

360
00:21:56,560 --> 00:21:58,470
<font color="yellow">I'll come by to your suite...</font>

361
00:21:58,470 --> 00:22:00,320
<font color="yellow">- this evening.
-  Shin Young.</font>

362
00:22:00,320 --> 00:22:03,350
<font color="yellow">Shut your mouth before I have the hotel recapitalised.</font>

363
00:22:17,590 --> 00:22:18,920
<font color="yellow">(Dodo Pharmaceutical Shares Drop)</font>

364
00:22:21,850 --> 00:22:23,790
<font color="yellow">- I won this time.
-  You did.</font>

365
00:22:23,790 --> 00:22:24,920
<font color="yellow">Well done.</font>

366
00:22:25,390 --> 00:22:27,520
<font color="yellow">Hey! Be quiet.</font>

367
00:22:28,790 --> 00:22:30,220
<font color="yellow">The mayor's reading the paper.</font>

368
00:22:36,590 --> 00:22:38,450
<font color="yellow">4984, you have a visitor.</font>

369
00:22:42,220 --> 00:22:43,450
<font color="yellow">Who could it be?</font>

370
00:22:43,820 --> 00:22:44,820
<font color="yellow">Gi Tan or Gun Woo?</font>

371
00:22:45,920 --> 00:22:47,990
<font color="yellow">I set them at each other's throats.</font>

372
00:22:48,590 --> 00:22:50,590
<font color="yellow">The wounded one would need my help.</font>

373
00:22:54,920 --> 00:22:56,420
<font color="yellow">You're here often.</font>

374
00:22:57,390 --> 00:22:59,990
<font color="yellow">Do you need my help?</font>

375
00:22:59,990 --> 00:23:02,220
<font color="yellow">You won't offer it even if I did.</font>

376
00:23:02,920 --> 00:23:06,190
<font color="yellow">If you're willing to get rid of Gi Tan for me,</font>

377
00:23:06,590 --> 00:23:07,920
<font color="yellow">I'd be willing to help you.</font>

378
00:23:08,320 --> 00:23:10,850
<font color="yellow">You'd say the same to Gi Tan if he were here.</font>

379
00:23:11,420 --> 00:23:14,890
<font color="yellow">"I'd be willing to help if you're willing to get rid of Gun Woo."</font>

380
00:23:17,890 --> 00:23:19,350
<font color="yellow">Why are you here?</font>

381
00:23:19,690 --> 00:23:20,920
<font color="yellow">You played on both sides.</font>

382
00:23:22,050 --> 00:23:23,490
<font color="yellow">Congratulations.</font>

383
00:23:28,220 --> 00:23:30,220
<font color="yellow">I thought long and hard about you.</font>

384
00:23:31,850 --> 00:23:34,050
<font color="yellow">"How much of you is real..."</font>

385
00:23:35,320 --> 00:23:37,090
<font color="yellow">"and how much is a mask?"</font>

386
00:23:38,390 --> 00:23:39,390
<font color="yellow">That's interesting.</font>

387
00:23:39,850 --> 00:23:40,850
<font color="yellow">And?</font>

388
00:23:41,520 --> 00:23:43,020
<font color="yellow">Your betraying me...</font>

389
00:23:43,690 --> 00:23:45,820
<font color="yellow">wasn't only because of Soo Yeon.</font>

390
00:23:48,850 --> 00:23:49,850
<font color="yellow">Did you...</font>

391
00:23:50,420 --> 00:23:52,650
<font color="yellow">come to Korea with the sole purpose of...</font>

392
00:23:53,150 --> 00:23:54,620
<font color="yellow">taking me down?</font>

393
00:23:59,720 --> 00:24:01,620
<font color="yellow">Do you still think...</font>

394
00:24:03,720 --> 00:24:05,950
<font color="yellow">I killed my stepfather by accident?</font>

395
00:24:39,520 --> 00:24:42,690
<font color="yellow">Where is your mum? Where is your mum?</font>

396
00:24:42,690 --> 00:24:44,020
<font color="yellow">I don't know.</font>

397
00:24:56,890 --> 00:24:58,300
<font color="yellow">I thought that...</font>

398
00:24:58,300 --> 00:25:00,290
<font color="yellow">if I only had the gun,</font>

399
00:25:00,290 --> 00:25:02,490
<font color="yellow">I could protect my mother from that monster.</font>

400
00:25:03,890 --> 00:25:04,890
<font color="yellow">But...</font>

401
00:25:05,320 --> 00:25:08,050
<font color="yellow">it took me 10 years to get a hold of that gun.</font>

402
00:25:09,120 --> 00:25:10,450
<font color="yellow">My stepfather...</font>

403
00:25:11,020 --> 00:25:13,290
<font color="yellow">was as suspicious as you are.</font>

404
00:25:17,520 --> 00:25:20,000
<font color="yellow">Come here, you dirty tramp!</font>

405
00:25:20,000 --> 00:25:21,020
<font color="yellow">That monster...</font>

406
00:25:21,520 --> 00:25:24,520
<font color="yellow">was high on drugs and alcohol, and started hitting my mother.</font>

407
00:25:24,520 --> 00:25:25,990
<font color="yellow">The time had come.</font>

408
00:25:31,420 --> 00:25:34,020
<font color="yellow">I could have pleaded self-defence.</font>

409
00:25:35,120 --> 00:25:36,520
<font color="yellow">- But...
-  Gun Woo.</font>

410
00:25:37,120 --> 00:25:38,120
<font color="yellow">That day,</font>

411
00:25:38,920 --> 00:25:40,350
<font color="yellow">you came by.</font>

412
00:25:41,020 --> 00:25:42,520
<font color="yellow">- Don't shoot.
-  They're here...</font>

413
00:25:42,850 --> 00:25:44,090
<font color="yellow">to see you.</font>

414
00:25:50,290 --> 00:25:52,120
<font color="yellow">I'll call you when the time is right.</font>

415
00:25:52,520 --> 00:25:56,120
<font color="yellow">Until then, use the fury inside to prepare yourself.</font>

416
00:25:57,690 --> 00:25:59,320
<font color="yellow">Turn your hatred for the world...</font>

417
00:26:00,620 --> 00:26:02,120
<font color="yellow">into ambition.</font>

418
00:26:02,790 --> 00:26:03,790
<font color="yellow">What do you say?</font>

419
00:26:04,220 --> 00:26:06,120
<font color="yellow">You only live once.</font>

420
00:26:08,020 --> 00:26:09,480
<font color="yellow">Isn't it worth a shot?</font>

421
00:26:09,480 --> 00:26:11,550
<font color="yellow">You planned to use me...</font>

422
00:26:12,050 --> 00:26:14,190
<font color="yellow">to swallow Dodo Group whole.</font>

423
00:26:16,920 --> 00:26:17,920
<font color="yellow">My plan...</font>

424
00:26:18,490 --> 00:26:19,890
<font color="yellow">was to use you...</font>

425
00:26:20,820 --> 00:26:22,820
<font color="yellow">to do the exact same thing.</font>

426
00:26:29,120 --> 00:26:30,120
<font color="yellow">You said...</font>

427
00:26:32,020 --> 00:26:35,050
<font color="yellow">you didn't want to become a monster like me.</font>

428
00:26:41,220 --> 00:26:42,590
<font color="yellow">Did you pretend...</font>

429
00:26:43,620 --> 00:26:45,420
<font color="yellow">to love Soo Yeon to deceive me?</font>

430
00:26:45,790 --> 00:26:47,990
<font color="yellow">There was one thing I didn't foresee.</font>

