524
00:32:04,890 --> 00:32:06,420
<font color="yellow">It's all because I'm incompetent.</font>

525
00:32:07,090 --> 00:32:08,320
<font color="yellow">You're not incompetent.</font>

526
00:32:09,090 --> 00:32:10,390
<font color="yellow">Don't ever say that.</font>

527
00:32:11,090 --> 00:32:12,270
<font color="yellow">Mum.</font>

528
00:32:12,270 --> 00:32:13,620
<font color="yellow">It's all my fault.</font>

529
00:32:14,750 --> 00:32:17,620
