00:36:25,620 --> 00:36:27,920
<font color="yellow">Honey! Gwi Ja!</font>

599
00:36:28,690 --> 00:36:31,120
<font color="yellow">I'm so sorry.</font>

600
00:36:31,650 --> 00:36:32,890
<font color="yellow">Where are you?</font>

