647
00:39:37,720 --> 00:39:38,790
<font color="yellow">Yes, Sir.</font>

648
00:39:48,850 --> 00:39:50,790
<font color="yellow">It's me, Han Sang Goo.</font>

649
00:39:52,290 --> 00:39:53,560
<font color="yellow">I was hurt.</font>

650
00:39:54,490 --> 00:39:56,350
<font color="yellow">You said you'd take me back.</font>

651
00:39:56,890 --> 00:39:58,670
<font color="yellow">Why did you avoid me?</font>

652
00:39:58,670 --> 00:40:01,930
<font color="yellow">I'm here right now, aren't I?</font>

653
00:40:01,930 --> 00:40:02,990
<font color="yellow">Forget it.</font>

654
00:40:03,490 --> 00:40:07,490
<font color="yellow">I can make a living without your help.</font>

655
00:40:07,490 --> 00:40:10,360
<font color="yellow">I need to ask for a favour.</font>

656
00:40:10,360 --> 00:40:12,190
<font color="yellow">Do you need a loan?</font>

657
00:40:13,220 --> 00:40:15,190
<font color="yellow">I charge a lot, you know?</font>

658
00:40:19,650 --> 00:40:20,690
<font color="yellow">Do Gun Woo.</font>

659
00:40:21,390 --> 00:40:22,790
<font color="yellow">Get rid of him for me.</font>

660
00:40:25,220 --> 00:40:28,790
<font color="yellow">I don't care if you kill him.</font>

661
00:40:32,290 --> 00:40:34,090
<font color="yellow">I don't do that any more.</font>

662
00:40:34,490 --> 00:40:36,490
<font color="yellow">- Please leave.
-  One large cheque.</font>

663
00:40:38,190 --> 00:40:41,220
<font color="yellow">How about that? Isn't it worth it now?</font>

664
00:40:43,020 --> 00:40:45,820
<font color="yellow">Everyone knows you're penniless.</font>

665
00:40:46,490 --> 00:40:48,470
<font color="yellow">Can you really pay up?</font>

666
00:40:48,470 --> 00:40:51,260
<font color="yellow">I'm Do Gwang Woo.</font>

667
00:40:51,260 --> 00:40:53,170
<font color="yellow">The heir of Dodo Group.</font>

668
00:40:53,170 --> 00:40:55,180
<font color="yellow">So what if you are?</font>

669
00:40:55,180 --> 00:40:57,990
<font color="yellow">I heard Do Gun Woo's the man in charge.</font>

670
00:40:57,990 --> 00:41:00,620
<font color="yellow">The company will be mine once he's out of the picture.</font>

671
00:41:01,150 --> 00:41:02,220
<font color="yellow">I'll pay you then.</font>

672
00:41:02,990 --> 00:41:07,060
<font color="yellow">I don't take after the fact payments.</font>

673
00:41:10,220 --> 00:41:12,390
<font color="yellow">Okay, then. 1.5 biggies.</font>

674
00:41:13,060 --> 00:41:14,150
<font color="yellow">I want 1.5 million.</font>

675
00:41:16,690 --> 00:41:19,210
<font color="yellow">Do you have to drive a hard bargain?</font>

676
00:41:19,210 --> 00:41:21,850
<font color="yellow">Take it or leave it. Find someone else.</font>

677
00:41:21,850 --> 00:41:22,920
<font color="yellow">Wait!</font>

678
00:41:24,390 --> 00:41:25,390
<font color="yellow">Fine.</font>

679
00:41:26,120 --> 00:41:27,120
<font color="yellow">1.5 million dollars.</font>

680
00:41:31,420 --> 00:41:32,420
<font color="yellow">Then...</font>

681
00:41:34,490 --> 00:41:36,590
<font color="yellow">Please sign this contract.</font>

682
00:41:42,790 --> 00:41:45,390
<font color="yellow">What... What's this?</font>

683
00:41:45,950 --> 00:41:47,150
<font color="yellow">"Waiver of Body Parts"?</font>

684
00:41:47,690 --> 00:41:48,870
<font color="yellow">I'm a loan shark.</font>

685
00:41:48,870 --> 00:41:52,120
<font color="yellow">Did you expect an insurance form?</font>

686
00:41:52,590 --> 00:41:53,620
<font color="yellow">You're funny.</font>

687
00:42:05,290 --> 00:42:07,590
<font color="yellow">Read it carefully before you sign it.</font>

688
00:42:07,590 --> 00:42:09,220
<font color="yellow">It's a serious document.</font>

689
00:42:20,150 --> 00:42:21,190
<font color="yellow">Promise that...</font>

690
00:42:21,950 --> 00:42:24,190
<font color="yellow">you won't mess this up.</font>

691
00:42:24,520 --> 00:42:27,420
<font color="yellow">Don't you worry. Just wire the money in time.</font>

692
00:42:37,020 --> 00:42:39,650
<font color="yellow">We have too little on B World.</font>

693
00:42:39,650 --> 00:42:42,210
<font color="yellow">This isn't enough to win the appeal.</font>

694
00:42:42,210 --> 00:42:45,150
<font color="yellow">I'm looking for more files. Give it some time.</font>

695
00:42:45,490 --> 00:42:47,850
<font color="yellow">The prosecutor in charge of the appeal...</font>

696
00:42:48,220 --> 00:42:49,290
<font color="yellow">Is he trustworthy?</font>

697
00:42:49,790 --> 00:42:51,370
<font color="yellow">I'm meeting him this evening.</font>

698
00:42:51,370 --> 00:42:54,350
<font color="yellow">You can see for yourself if you care to join me.</font>

699
00:42:55,690 --> 00:42:57,120
<font color="yellow">- Soo Yeon.
-  Yes, Gi...</font>

700
00:43:04,950 --> 00:43:06,650
<font color="yellow">I heard we used to be close.</font>

701
00:43:09,520 --> 00:43:13,650
<font color="yellow">He saw a photo you two took when you worked at Dodo Group.</font>

702
00:43:16,020 --> 00:43:17,390
<font color="yellow">Could you excuse us?</font>

703
00:43:18,090 --> 00:43:19,150
<font color="yellow">Yes, Sir.</font>

704
00:43:34,220 --> 00:43:35,290
<font color="yellow">I heard...</font>

705
00:43:37,220 --> 00:43:39,490
<font color="yellow">your brother died because of me.</font>

706
00:43:43,490 --> 00:43:44,490
<font color="yellow">I'm sorry.</font>

707
00:43:45,990 --> 00:43:47,950
<font color="yellow">I found out too late.</font>

708
00:43:50,150 --> 00:43:51,420
<font color="yellow">It's in the past.</font>

709
00:43:51,990 --> 00:43:53,480
<font color="yellow">Don't concern yourself.</font>

710
00:43:53,480 --> 00:43:54,620
<font color="yellow">Dong Soo, was it?</font>

711
00:43:55,490 --> 00:43:56,490
<font color="yellow">His name, I mean.</font>

712
00:43:59,220 --> 00:44:00,220
<font color="yellow">If you don't mind,</font>

713
00:44:01,890 --> 00:44:04,150
<font color="yellow">I'd like to visit his place at the charnel house.</font>

714
00:44:04,850 --> 00:44:06,200
<font color="yellow">You don't have to.</font>

715
00:44:06,200 --> 00:44:08,150
<font color="yellow">We used to be friends.</font>

716
00:44:09,120 --> 00:44:12,020
<font color="yellow">How about we speak freely like we used to?</font>

717
00:44:13,790 --> 00:44:16,220
<font color="yellow">It must feel awkward trying to be polite to a friend.</font>

718
00:44:16,220 --> 00:44:17,650
<font color="yellow">I prefer things as it is right now.</font>

719
00:44:20,590 --> 00:44:23,850
<font color="yellow">I'll have no reason to see you after Il Jae's trial.</font>

720
00:44:24,220 --> 00:44:25,290
<font color="yellow">Are you...</font>

721
00:44:27,390 --> 00:44:28,820
<font color="yellow">afraid I'll suffer?</font>

722
00:44:38,990 --> 00:44:39,990
<font color="yellow">Prosecutor Choi.</font>

723
00:44:41,150 --> 00:44:42,550
<font color="yellow">We'll leave right now.</font>

724
00:44:43,190 --> 00:44:44,190
<font color="yellow">Sure.</font>

725
00:44:51,890 --> 00:44:54,500
<font color="yellow">What is Prosecutor Choi like?</font>

726
00:44:54,500 --> 00:44:58,730
<font color="yellow">His peers know him for being upright and honest.</font>

727
00:44:58,730 --> 00:45:00,320
<font color="yellow">My prosecutor contact said...</font>

728
00:45:00,320 --> 00:45:04,290
<font color="yellow">he has enemies because he's so transparent.</font>

729
00:45:05,990 --> 00:45:07,290
<font color="yellow">Then we can trust him.</font>

730
00:45:09,490 --> 00:45:10,790
<font color="yellow">Prosecutor Choi is here.</font>

731
00:45:12,420 --> 00:45:13,790
<font color="yellow">Hello.</font>

732
00:45:14,750 --> 00:45:16,920
<font color="yellow">- I'm Kang Gi Tan.
-  I'm Moon Tae Gwang.</font>

733
00:45:16,920 --> 00:45:17,980
<font color="yellow">Hello.</font>

734
00:45:17,980 --> 00:45:20,390
<font color="yellow">Lawyer Oh told me a lot about you.</font>

735
00:45:20,750 --> 00:45:21,750
<font color="yellow">Have a seat.</font>

736
00:45:27,750 --> 00:45:30,090
<font color="yellow">I went over the files you sent.</font>

737
00:45:31,020 --> 00:45:34,140
<font color="yellow">Il Jae is worse than I thought.</font>

738
00:45:34,140 --> 00:45:35,720
<font color="yellow">If you knew him,</font>

739
00:45:35,720 --> 00:45:38,590
<font color="yellow">you'd be even more shocked.</font>

740
00:45:38,590 --> 00:45:40,990
<font color="yellow">I find it embarrassing and infuriating that...</font>

741
00:45:41,690 --> 00:45:43,190
<font color="yellow">he used to be a fellow prosecutor.</font>

742
00:45:43,190 --> 00:45:45,150
<font color="yellow">He has many contacts.</font>

743
00:45:46,220 --> 00:45:47,290
<font color="yellow">I hope that...</font>

744
00:45:48,050 --> 00:45:50,290
<font color="yellow">you won't give in to pressure.</font>

745
00:45:50,290 --> 00:45:51,350
<font color="yellow">Don't worry.</font>

746
00:45:51,790 --> 00:45:54,420
<font color="yellow">I'm not the kind of person who gives in to temptation.</font>

747
00:46:04,890 --> 00:46:05,890
<font color="yellow">Hello?</font>

748
00:46:06,750 --> 00:46:08,220
<font color="yellow">I'm away from the office.</font>

749
00:46:16,090 --> 00:46:18,120
<font color="yellow">Can I come in, Sir?</font>

750
00:46:18,790 --> 00:46:19,790
<font color="yellow">Come in.</font>

751
00:46:26,850 --> 00:46:27,890
<font color="yellow">Welcome.</font>

752
00:46:28,890 --> 00:46:29,950
<font color="yellow">You must know...</font>

753
00:46:30,520 --> 00:46:31,520
<font color="yellow">Congressman Hwang Jae Man.</font>

754
00:46:32,190 --> 00:46:34,290
<font color="yellow">Hello, Sir. I'm Choi Jeong Gook.</font>

755
00:46:36,690 --> 00:46:39,500
<font color="yellow">This is his daughter, Congresswoman Hwang Ji Soo.</font>

756
00:46:39,500 --> 00:46:40,850
<font color="yellow">I'm pleased to meet you.</font>

757
00:46:42,420 --> 00:46:43,890
<font color="yellow">Take a seat.</font>

758
00:46:48,390 --> 00:46:51,720
<font color="yellow">He was a rookie when I was a deputy-chief prosecutor.</font>

759
00:46:52,290 --> 00:46:53,290
<font color="yellow">That's when...</font>

760
00:46:54,050 --> 00:46:56,090
<font color="yellow">I noticed his potentials.</font>

761
00:46:59,490 --> 00:47:00,750
<font color="yellow">Next week,</font>

762
00:47:02,090 --> 00:47:04,750
<font color="yellow">I will announce that I will seek my party's nomination...</font>

763
00:47:05,320 --> 00:47:07,200
<font color="yellow">to run for presidency.</font>

764
00:47:07,200 --> 00:47:08,860
<font color="yellow">Yes, I'm aware of that.</font>

765
00:47:08,860 --> 00:47:10,020
<font color="yellow">But it just so happens that...</font>

766
00:47:10,420 --> 00:47:14,190
<font color="yellow">my son-in-law's trial begins on the same day.</font>

767
00:47:15,850 --> 00:47:16,850
<font color="yellow">You control...</font>

768
00:47:17,650 --> 00:47:20,190
<font color="yellow">the future of my campaign and our country.</font>

769
00:47:21,390 --> 00:47:23,290
<font color="yellow">Do you get what I mean?</font>

770
00:47:24,190 --> 00:47:25,210
<font color="yellow">Yes, Sir.</font>

771
00:47:25,210 --> 00:47:27,550
<font color="yellow">If Mr Hwang becomes President,</font>

772
00:47:28,420 --> 00:47:31,550
<font color="yellow">he will make you the youngest ever superintendent public prosecutor.</font>

773
00:47:32,220 --> 00:47:34,920
<font color="yellow">You could go even higher than that.</font>

774
00:47:36,590 --> 00:47:40,150
<font color="yellow">Don't say such a thing, Mr Jang.</font>

775
00:47:42,520 --> 00:47:44,220
<font color="yellow">I'll be direct.</font>

776
00:47:44,950 --> 00:47:47,550
<font color="yellow">This appeal to the Supreme Court...</font>

777
00:47:48,320 --> 00:47:49,720
<font color="yellow">Please turn it down.</font>

778
00:47:51,490 --> 00:47:52,650
<font color="yellow">I will.</font>

779
00:47:52,990 --> 00:47:53,990
<font color="yellow">Let me...</font>

780
00:47:54,590 --> 00:47:56,020
<font color="yellow">pour you a drink.</font>

781
00:47:59,390 --> 00:48:00,720
<font color="yellow">Here you go.</font>

782
00:48:16,220 --> 00:48:17,220
<font color="yellow">Sir.</font>

783
00:48:20,320 --> 00:48:21,350
<font color="yellow">I have it.</font>

784
00:48:33,950 --> 00:48:35,190
<font color="yellow">Will you really...</font>

785
00:48:35,190 --> 00:48:37,220
<font color="yellow">give this to Lawyer Oh?</font>

786
00:48:37,950 --> 00:48:39,860
<font color="yellow">It's me. Where are you?</font>

787
00:48:39,860 --> 00:48:42,290
<font color="yellow">At my office. Is something wrong?</font>

788
00:48:42,290 --> 00:48:44,490
<font color="yellow">I found evidence of Il Jae's corruption.</font>

789
00:48:45,890 --> 00:48:48,850
<font color="yellow">I'll give this to you. Let's meet right now.</font>

790
00:48:48,850 --> 00:48:51,050
<font color="yellow">Okay. Where should I go?</font>

791
00:48:52,020 --> 00:48:54,290
<font color="yellow">I know that place. I'll be there.</font>

792
00:48:56,420 --> 00:48:58,550
<font color="yellow">Gun Woo found evidence of Il Jae's B World corruption.</font>

793
00:48:59,090 --> 00:49:00,720
<font color="yellow">I told you...</font>

794
00:49:00,720 --> 00:49:02,390
<font color="yellow">that Gun Woo would find it.</font>

795
00:49:02,390 --> 00:49:05,050
<font color="yellow">You were right. We didn't need to do this.</font>

796
00:49:05,620 --> 00:49:06,950
<font color="yellow">I'll be back.</font>

797
00:49:07,890 --> 00:49:09,020
<font color="yellow">Oh, wait.</font>

798
00:49:09,950 --> 00:49:12,950
<font color="yellow">Be nice to Gun Woo.</font>

799
00:49:12,950 --> 00:49:17,050
<font color="yellow">Think about it. He's helped you out very often.</font>

800
00:49:17,420 --> 00:49:19,620
<font color="yellow">- I'll be back.
-  Okay.</font>

801
00:49:45,220 --> 00:49:46,820
<font color="yellow">- Follow him.
-  Okay.</font>

802
00:50:05,520 --> 00:50:06,520
<font color="yellow">Yes.</font>

803
00:50:12,020 --> 00:50:13,820
<font color="yellow">We're following Gun Woo.</font>

804
00:50:13,820 --> 00:50:15,320
<font color="yellow">Don't make a mistake.</font>

805
00:50:15,320 --> 00:50:17,290
<font color="yellow">One mistake will kill us all.</font>

806
00:50:19,050 --> 00:50:20,050
<font color="yellow">Okay. Take care.</font>

807
00:50:35,050 --> 00:50:36,050
<font color="yellow">Chairman.</font>

808
00:50:37,990 --> 00:50:40,350
<font color="yellow">I found Dong Soo's charnel house.</font>

809
00:51:02,590 --> 00:51:04,550
<font color="yellow">- Gun Woo.
-  Hey.</font>

810
00:51:07,920 --> 00:51:10,350
<font color="yellow">Stay there. I'll go over.</font>

811
00:51:19,490 --> 00:51:20,550
<font color="yellow">Who are you?</font>

812
00:51:27,290 --> 00:51:28,320
<font color="yellow">Gun Woo.</font>

813
00:51:37,450 --> 00:51:38,590
<font color="yellow">Gun Woo!</font>

814
00:51:42,350 --> 00:51:44,130
<font color="yellow">Gun Woo. Gun Woo.</font>

815
00:51:44,130 --> 00:51:45,290
<font color="yellow">Gun Woo.</font>

816
00:51:45,290 --> 00:51:47,990
<font color="yellow">I think I was stabbed with a knife.</font>

817
00:51:49,950 --> 00:51:51,550
<font color="yellow">Please help us!</font>

818
00:51:51,550 --> 00:51:52,790
<font color="yellow">Is anyone there?</font>

819
00:51:54,190 --> 00:51:55,620
<font color="yellow">Gun Woo, hang in there.</font>

820
00:51:56,750 --> 00:51:59,820
<font color="yellow">Help us! We need help!</font>

821
00:52:02,350 --> 00:52:03,520
<font color="yellow">That's...</font>

822
00:52:04,020 --> 00:52:05,920
<font color="yellow">Lawyer Oh's little brother.</font>

823
00:52:11,020 --> 00:52:13,050
<font color="yellow">My beloved brother, Dong Soo.</font>

824
00:52:13,690 --> 00:52:15,420
<font color="yellow">Don't ever get sick again...</font>

825
00:52:15,920 --> 00:52:17,960
<font color="yellow">and rest well up there.</font>

826
00:52:17,960 --> 00:52:20,220
<font color="yellow">I can't believe I had no idea...</font>

827
00:52:21,550 --> 00:52:23,050
<font color="yellow">when I've hurt her this deeply.</font>

828
00:52:23,450 --> 00:52:26,320
<font color="yellow">It's not your fault, Chairman. Don't blame yourself.</font>

829
00:52:41,290 --> 00:52:42,320
<font color="yellow">Since when...</font>

830
00:52:43,350 --> 00:52:45,190
<font color="yellow">did I have this necklace on?</font>

831
00:52:45,890 --> 00:52:48,790
<font color="yellow">I don't know.</font>

832
00:52:50,290 --> 00:52:51,890
<font color="yellow">His necklace and mine...</font>

833
00:52:53,450 --> 00:52:54,820
<font color="yellow">are the same.</font>

834
00:52:55,590 --> 00:52:57,950
<font color="yellow">There are a lot of the same necklaces.</font>

835
00:52:58,290 --> 00:53:01,050
<font color="yellow">But not a lot of men wear women's necklaces.</font>

836
00:53:03,350 --> 00:53:04,890
<font color="yellow">It's definitely the same necklace.</font>

837
00:53:19,550 --> 00:53:21,290
<font color="yellow">Gun Woo, hang in there.</font>

838
00:53:22,120 --> 00:53:24,020
<font color="yellow">Stay with me, Gun Woo.</font>

839
00:53:26,150 --> 00:53:27,450
<font color="yellow">Gun Woo, hold on.</font>

840
00:53:30,320 --> 00:53:31,450
<font color="yellow">(Kang Gi Tan)</font>

841
00:53:32,150 --> 00:53:37,650
<font color="yellow">Your call has been forwarded to an automated voice messaging...</font>

842
00:53:43,450 --> 00:53:45,690
<font color="yellow">Gun Woo, can you hear me?</font>

843
00:53:46,450 --> 00:53:47,820
<font color="yellow">Gun Woo, look at me.</font>

844
00:53:50,090 --> 00:53:51,090
<font color="yellow">Gun Woo.</font>

845
00:53:53,220 --> 00:53:54,320
<font color="yellow">You can't go in.</font>

846
00:53:56,120 --> 00:53:58,150
<font color="yellow">(Emergency Room)</font>

847
00:53:58,150 --> 00:53:59,320
<font color="yellow">Gun Woo.</font>

848
00:54:07,220 --> 00:54:08,220
<font color="yellow">Hello?</font>

849
00:54:09,190 --> 00:54:10,290
<font color="yellow">Soo Yeon?</font>

850
00:54:11,350 --> 00:54:13,390
<font color="yellow">Who is it? Chairman Kang.</font>

851
00:54:16,750 --> 00:54:17,890
<font color="yellow">I'm sorry to bother you so late.</font>

852
00:54:18,790 --> 00:54:21,420
<font color="yellow">- Is Soo Yeon here?
-  She's not.</font>

853
00:54:21,420 --> 00:54:23,390
<font color="yellow">She's not at the office either and won't pick up her phone.</font>

854
00:54:24,120 --> 00:54:25,540
<font color="yellow">Is everything all right?</font>

855
00:54:25,540 --> 00:54:28,370
<font color="yellow">She went to meet CEO Do to receive evidence...</font>

856
00:54:28,370 --> 00:54:30,020
<font color="yellow">of Il Jae's corruption.</font>

857
00:54:30,520 --> 00:54:31,620
<font color="yellow">Gun Woo?</font>

858
00:54:46,090 --> 00:54:49,920
<font color="yellow">Tax evasion and embezzlement. He took a lot of money.</font>

859
00:54:51,690 --> 00:54:53,620
<font color="yellow">Great job.</font>

860
00:54:54,420 --> 00:54:56,550
<font color="yellow">Go overseas for a while until everything is settled.</font>

861
00:54:56,550 --> 00:54:57,550
<font color="yellow">Yes, Boss.</font>

862
00:55:05,120 --> 00:55:06,150
<font color="yellow">Hello, Sir.</font>

